 px-4 text-gray-700 text-sm md:text-base">High adoption is essential</td></tr><tr class="border-t border-gray-200 hover:bg-gray-50 transition"><td class="py-3 px-4 text-gray-900 text-sm md:text-base">Exception rate</td><td class="py-3 px-4 text-gray-700 text-sm md:text-base">Cases falling outside coverage</td><td class="py-3 px-4 text-gray-700 text-sm md:text-base">Should decrease over time</td></tr><tr class="border-t border-gray-200 hover:bg-gray-50 transition"><td class="py-3 px-4 text-gray-900 text-sm md:text-base">ROI</td><td class="py-3 px-4 text-gray-700 text-sm md:text-base">Value delivered vs investment</td><td class="py-3 px-4 text-gray-700 text-sm md:text-base">Break-even within 6–18 months</td></tr><tr class="border-t border-gray-200 hover:bg-gray-50 transition"><td class="py-3 px-4 text-gray-900 text-sm md:text-base">Cycle time / lead time</td><td class="py-3 px-4 text-gray-700 text-sm md:text-base">Total end-to-end time</td><td class="py-3 px-4 text-gray-700 text-sm md:text-base">Shorter, smoother flows</td></tr></tbody></table></div><div class="mt-6 bg-[#F0F3FF] border-l-4 border-[#D9E2FF] p-4 rounded-md text-gray-800 text-sm md:text-base"><strong>Pro Tip:</strong> <!-- -->Use cohort analysis — track before/after for the same tasks to truly see impact, not just cross-sectional snapshots.</div></div><aside class="lg:pl-4"><div class="sticky top-24 border border-gray-200 rounded-lg p-5 bg-gray-50"><ul class="space-y-2 text-sm font-medium text-gray-700"><li class="">The Burden of Manual Work</li><li class="">What the Numbers Say</li><li class="">Why Projects Fail</li><li class="">Effective Principles</li><li class="">Strategy Playbook</li><li class="text-[#2B4DDF] font-semibold">Metrics &amp; KPIs</li><li class="">Technology Requirements</li><li class="">How AiBit Soft Helps</li><li class="">Final Thoughts</li></ul></div></aside></div></div></section><section class="bg-white py-7 px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8"><div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 md:px-8 lg:px-[80p